{"type":"message","id":"4bf028be","parentId":"4ab8a3ab","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:45:04.898Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to read the configuration file to understand what stock monitoring tasks to execute.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f80a8641da8b426f8306a207","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data-cron-config.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773117900067}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc9a510e","parentId":"4bf028be","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:45:04.901Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_f80a8641da8b426f8306a207","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 实时数据获取操作\n\n**重要提示**\n- 你的工作路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock\n- 自定义文件路径：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock\n- 你独享的skill存放位置：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/skills\n- 以下描述中没有具体位置的文件都是自定义文件，存放在自定义路径下，\n  如'realtime-data.txt'实际路径为：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt；\n- 指定了具体路径的文件，按照指定路径读取，如：~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md；\n- 如果你需要新建文件，统一存放在自定义路径下；\n- 如果存在可用脚本，优先复用，不满足当前场景时才允许创建新脚本。\n- 执行时严格按照要求的文件名称及后缀，防止执行到不存在的文件。\n\n### 操作流程\n\n1、使用tushare-data skill，获取数据判断今日是否收盘，未收盘，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务；\n2、如果realtime-data.txt里的内容不为空，则清空后进行下一步；否则直接进行下一步；\n3、阅读~/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md内的skill使用说明，严格按照要求使用skill；\n4、使用tushare-data skill，按照get-data-template.md内的格式要求获取自选股的实时数据，保存在realtime-data.txt里；\n5、按照alert-rules.md中的预警规则和以下条件过滤获取到的实时数据：\n   - 满足预警规则中任意一条条件；\n   - 只返回满足预警规则的数据；\n6、如果存在满足条件的数据，则进行下一步；否则，结束本次任务。\n7、读取receiver-list.txt接受者用户列表文件，使用命令openclaw message broadcast --channel feishu --account stock --targets <user_id1> --targets <user_id2>... --message <xxx>，\n   将预警数据通过飞书(feishu)渠道推送给列表文件中的用户；\n   - --targets <user_id> 参数可重复\n8、推送的数据格式参考alert-template.md的内容要求。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773117904900}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f4805d6","parentId":"cc9a510e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:45:09.839Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要读取配置文件引用的相关文件来了解具体的数据格式、预警规则和推送模板要求。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5beff79f9cbf4ec39a66c2fd","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/get-data-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4786c9c8b2894d74ad407314","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-rules.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2e81fba93b64461d920c5ed3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/alert-template.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3d49045d285c426f8efd3b23","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/receiver-list.txt"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bd4b2c9357284d4c90a0901e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/stock/realtime-data.txt"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6245b3bb72734335b4feef4a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock/TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773117904901}}
{"type":"message","id":"ec215036","parentId":"0f4805d6","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:45:09.842Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_5beff79f9cbf4ec39a66c2fd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 数据获取模板\n\n按照以下格式获取【我的自选股票】的最新行情数据：\n\n【必选字段】\n1. 代码 (Stock Code) - 6 位数字/字母组合\n2. 名称 (Stock Name) - 中文全称\n3. 当前股价 (Current Price) - ¥XX.XX 元\n4. 涨跌幅 (Change %) - +X.XX% / -X.XX%\n5. 涨跌额(Price Change) - ¥XX.XX 元\n5. 时间点 (Timestamp) - YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS\n\n【可选字段 - 根据需求添加】\n- 昨收价 (Previous Close)\n- 今开价 (Open Price)\n- 最高价 (High)\n- 最低价 (Low)\n- 成交量 (Volume)\n- 成交额 (Amount)\n- 市盈率 (PE Ratio)\n- 总市值 (Market Cap)\n- 涨跌额 (Price Change)\n- 换手率 (Turnover Rate)\n\n【数据源要求】\n- 优先级：Tushare Pro > 东方财富 > 同花顺\n- 实时性：优先使用盘口最新报价\n- 准确性：需交叉验证（建议用网页端确认）\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773117909840}}
{"type":"message","id":"02cd4141","parentId":"ec215036","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:45:09.844Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4786c9c8b2894d74ad407314","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警规则\n\n### 通用规则\n1、下跌 > 3% → 触发\n2、上涨 > 5% → 触发\n\n### 个股专属规则\n**中国石油 (601857.SH)**:\n- 🟢 涨幅 > 2% → 触发预警\n- 🔴 跌幅 > 1% → 触发预警\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773117909843}}
{"type":"message","id":"6bc3b711","parentId":"02cd4141","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:45:09.847Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2e81fba93b64461d920c5ed3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773117909845}}
