{"type":"message","id":"524df99a","parentId":"2c0c8877","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:45:20.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"需要按照配置流程第一步使用 tushare-data skill 判断今日是否收盘，编写 Python 脚本来获取交易日历和实时行情数据进行判断。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我需要按照配置文件的流程执行任务。让我先检查今天是否已收盘，然后获取实时数据。\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_32dac59206694a0ca1eb8a04","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'EOF'\nimport os\nimport tushare as ts\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 获取 token\ntoken = os.getenv('TUSHARE_TOKEN')\nif not token:\n    print(\"未找到 TUSHARE_TOKEN 环境变量\")\n    exit(1)\n\n# 初始化 pro 接口\npro = ts.pro_api(token)\n\n# 获取交易日历，判断今天是否交易日且已收盘\ntoday = datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d')\ncal_df = pro.trade_cal(exchange='SSE', start_date=today, end_date=today, fields='cal_date,is_open')\n\nif cal_df.empty or cal_df.iloc[0]['is_open'] == 0:\n    print(\"今日非交易日\")\n    exit(0)\n\n# 获取当前时间，判断是否已收盘（A 股 15:00 收盘）\ncurrent_time = datetime.now()\nmarket_close = current_time.replace(hour=15, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)\n\nif current_time < market_close:\n    print(\"未收盘\")\nelse:\n    print(\"已收盘\")\nEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773117912111}}
