{"type":"message","id":"9903e531","parentId":"ee98b00f","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:49:32.876Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"数据已保存成功，现在需要按照 alert-rules.md 中的预警规则过滤数据，筛选出满足条件的股票。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"数据已保存。现在我需要按照 alert-rules.md 的预警规则过滤数据：\n\n**预警规则：**\n- 通用规则：下跌 > 3% 或 上涨 > 5%\n- 中国石油 (601857): 涨幅 > 2% 或 跌幅 > 1%\n\n让我过滤满足条件的股票：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b4c10285bd9a404f9aedae33","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 读取实时数据\nstocks = []\nwith open('stock/realtime-data.txt', 'r') as f:\n    header = f.readline()  # 跳过表头\n    for line in f:\n        line = line.strip()\n        if line:\n            parts = line.split('|')\n            if len(parts) >= 12:\n                stocks.append({\n                    'code': parts[0],\n                    'name': parts[1],\n                    'current_price': float(parts[2]),\n                    'change_pct': float(parts[3]),\n                    'change_amt': float(parts[4]),\n                    'timestamp': parts[11]\n                })\n\nprint(f\"共读取 {len(stocks)} 只股票数据\")\n\n# 预警规则过滤\nalert_stocks = []\n\nfor stock in stocks:\n    code = stock['code']\n    change_pct = stock['change_pct']\n    triggered = False\n    reason = []\n    \n    # 中国石油专属规则\n    if code == '601857':\n        if change_pct > 2:\n            triggered = True\n            reason.append(f\"🟢 涨幅 {change_pct:.2f}% > 2%\")\n        elif change_pct < -1:\n            triggered = True\n            reason.append(f\"🔴 跌幅 {change_pct:.2f}% > 1%\")\n    else:\n        # 通用规则\n        if change_pct < -3:\n            triggered = True\n            reason.append(f\"📉 下跌 {change_pct:.2f}% > 3%\")\n        elif change_pct > 5:\n            triggered = True\n            reason.append(f\"📈 上涨 {change_pct:.2f}% > 5%\")\n    \n    if triggered:\n        stock['alert_reason'] = reason\n        alert_stocks.append(stock)\n        print(f\"⚠️ {stock['name']} ({code}): {change_pct:+.2f}% - {', '.join(reason)}\")\n\n# 按涨跌幅排序\nalert_stocks.sort(key=lambda x: x['change_pct'], reverse=True)\n\nprint(f\"\\n共 {len(alert_stocks)} 只股票触发预警\")\n\n# 保存到预警文件\nwith open('stock/alert-stocks.txt', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(\"code|name|current_price|change_pct|change_amt|timestamp|reason\\n\")\n    for s in alert_stocks:\n        reason_str = '; '.join(s['alert_reason'])\n        f.write(f\"{s['code']}|{s['name']}|{s['current_price']:.2f}|{s['change_pct']:.2f}|{s['change_amt']:.2f}|{s['timestamp']}|{reason_str}\\n\")\n\nprint(\"预警数据已保存到 stock/alert-stocks.txt\")\nPYEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773118160031}}
