{"type":"message","id":"31124b8a","parentId":"5cebb65e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:49:38.236Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8f30f0b73d9741e89800ed86","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 预警数据输出模版\n\n【输出格式】\n表格形式，每页输出10条数据,按涨跌幅排序，高亮异常波动\n\n示例：\n| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额| 时间 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|-------|------|\n| XXXX | XXXX | ¥XX.XX | +X.XX% |￥XXXX |12:00 |\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > x% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > x% → 触发\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773118178234}}
{"type":"message","id":"867984f8","parentId":"31124b8a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:49:52.402Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"已获取接收者列表和预警模板，现在需要构建符合模板格式的飞书消息并执行广播推送。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在构建预警消息并推送。根据模板要求，使用表格形式展示数据：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4747962e6e4147c8a7984a4c","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/openclaw/.openclaw/workspace-main-stock && python3 << 'PYEOF'\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\n# 读取预警数据\nalert_stocks = []\nwith open('stock/alert-stocks.txt', 'r') as f:\n    header = f.readline()  # 跳过表头\n    for line in f:\n        line = line.strip()\n        if line:\n            parts = line.split('|')\n            if len(parts) >= 7:\n                alert_stocks.append({\n                    'code': parts[0],\n                    'name': parts[1],\n                    'current_price': float(parts[2]),\n                    'change_pct': float(parts[3]),\n                    'change_amt': float(parts[4]),\n                    'timestamp': parts[5],\n                    'reason': parts[6]\n                })\n\n# 按涨跌幅排序\nalert_stocks.sort(key=lambda x: x['change_pct'], reverse=True)\n\n# 构建消息\ncurrent_time = datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M')\ndate_str = datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d')\n\n# 构建表格\ntable_lines = []\ntable_lines.append(\"| 代码 | 名称 | 当前价 | 涨跌幅 | 涨跌额 | 时间 |\")\ntable_lines.append(\"|------|------|--------|--------|--------|------|\")\n\nfor stock in alert_stocks:\n    change_str = f\"{stock['change_pct']:+.2f}%\"\n    price_str = f\"¥{stock['current_price']:.2f}\"\n    amt_str = f\"¥{stock['change_amt']:.2f}\"\n    time_str = stock['timestamp'].split(' ')[1][:5]  # 只取 HH:MM\n    \n    table_lines.append(f\"| {stock['code']} | {stock['name']} | {price_str} | {change_str} | {amt_str} | {time_str} |\")\n\ntable_text = '\\n'.join(table_lines)\n\n# 构建完整消息\nmessage = f\"\"\"📊 股票预警通知 - {date_str} {current_time}\n\n{table_text}\n\n⚙️ 预警规则\n• 📉 下跌 > 3% → 触发\n• 📈 上涨 > 5% → 触发\n• 🔴 中国石油：跌幅 > 1% → 触发\n\n⏰ 数据时间：{current_time}\n📈 数据来源：腾讯财经\"\"\"\n\nprint(\"预警消息内容:\")\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\nprint(message)\nprint(\"=\" * 60)\n\n# 保存消息到文件\nwith open('stock/last-alert-message.txt', 'w') as f:\n    f.write(message)\n\nprint(\"\\n消息已保存到 stock/last-alert-message.txt\")\nPYEOF\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-397b-a17b","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773118178236}}
